dateText:
January
Sun
25

Did not go to Church -- Mary did - and saw that Mrs. Gannett was quite ill - almost fainted before going to the Chapel -
fullText: Did not go to Church -- Mary did - and saw that Mrs. Gannett was quite ill - almost fainted before going to the Chapel -
summaryText: Mary went to church and saw that Mrs. Gannett was quite ill.
